FBIS4-37268 "drnes118_j_94039" FBIS-NES-94-118 Daily Report 19 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Aden Source Vows Escalation If Ibrahimi Fails Aden Source Vows Escalation If Ibrahimi Fails NC1906163594 London MBC Television in Arabic 1600 GMT 19 Jun 94 NC1906163594 London MBC Television Arabic BFN [Text] A responsbile source in the Democratic Republic of Yemen said that if the mission of UN Envoy Lakhdar Ibrahimi fails to stop the fighting in Yemen, the south Yemeni naval and air forces will concentrate their attacks on vital targets in north Yemen. The source accused the Sanaa government of pursuing a policy of procrastination regarding the UN endeavors.
